mystery photographs

Every once in a while someone turns up a wonderful old photograph with no identification on it! We are sure all the photos shown here are connected to us in one way or another--we just don't know which way. We've had some success in the past with other family members recognizing a face or a location. Occasionally someone else has a copy of the same picture with a name written on the back. Any help you can give us in identifying theses pictures will be greatly appreciated. Please also let us know if you can add any photos to our family archive (and, if they are identified, we will be really happy). Click on the thumbnail view here to see a larger version of the picture. Then click "back" on your browser to return to this page.
